  <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--sui-text-light);margin-bottom:16px;">Constrain selectable dates with <code>data-sui-min</code> and <code>data-sui-max</code>. Accepts <code>"today"</code> or a date string like <code>"2026-06-15"</code> (YYYY-MM-DD). Dates outside the range are disabled.</p>
