<div class="pg-section" id="section-8">
  <h3 class="pg-section-title">Time Picker</h3>
  <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--sui-text-light);margin-bottom:16px;">A standalone time picker without a calendar. Use <code>data-sui-timepicker</code> for 12-hour format or <code>data-sui-timepicker="24h"</code> for 24-hour. Arrow keys increment/decrement values. Fires a <code>sui-time-change</code> event.</p>
  <div class="pg-section-row" style="justify-content:center;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
